subtitleNullable: Dataset with images of all the characters from the Dragon Ball Anime Series
descriptionNullable:
### Content

This is an image dataset which contains images of all the characters from the Dragon Ball Series. This includes characters from Dragon Ball, Dragon Ball Z and Dragon Ball Super. The dataset is being regularly updated.


### Acknowledgements

These images were taken from Google and Bing Images. I do not own any of these images.


### Inspiration

The Dragon Ball Series is one of the most popular Anime series out there and one of my favorites while growing up.
